Write .agents/handoffs/handoff.md.
Assume the next decision agent already has the complete project plan.
Capture only the essential operational knowledge gained during this slice.
Focus on where execution refined, validated, challenged, or otherwise changed the understanding of the planned work.
Include:
- meaningful changes to the project's operational understanding
- active decisions that continue to shape future execution
- unresolved questions or newly discovered risks
- the single recommended next objective
Exclude implementation history, routine progress, and details that do not materially affect future decisions.